Algorithm:
1. Start
2. Input the temperature in Celsius (C).
3. Calculate Fahrenheit using the formula:
F = (C \times 9/5) + 32
5. End

Pseudocode:
START
PRINT "Enter temperature in Celsius:"
INPUT C
SET F = (C * 9/5) + 32
PRINT "Temperature in Fahrenheit is:", F
STOP

Flowchart:
    A[Start] --> B[Input temperature in Celsius (C)]
    B --> C[Calculate F = (C Ã— 9/5) + 32]
    C --> D[Output temperature in Fahrenheit (F)]
    D --> E[End]
